caja-open-terminal (0.9-1) experimental; urgency=low

  * New upstream release: 
    + Use GIO instead of MateVFS
    + Add MateConf key for deciding whether right-clicking the
      desktop opens home directory or desktop directory
      (Closes: #400297)
    + Use remote $SHELL instead of /bin/sh for SFTP terminals. 
    + Use Caja extension directory from libcaja-extension.pc
    + Bugfixes
    + Added and updated translations
  * Removed mateconf-exec-key.diff (merged upstream)

 -- Julien Valroff <julien@kirya.net>  Sat, 05 Mar 2008 20:04:59 +0200

